title: Insiders Buy the Holdings of VYM ETF - Nasdaq.com
text: A look at the weighted underlying holdings of the Vanguard High Dividend Yield ETF (Symbol: VYM) shows an impressive 10.1% of holdings on a weighted basis have experienced insider buying within the past six months.
